Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Motoba is fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,0:02:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah, so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In third place, from Arayada High School: Motoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Motoba has just placed third\Nin the Prefectural Tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie is great, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the fastest swimmer in our school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is impressive indeed, Kirie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, both of you take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job, Motoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You were faster than the third-years!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, you have a future as a pro swimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it, but maybe talking about\Nbeing a pro swimmer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's a BAD thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's all the pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As in, using the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, look! I placed third in a swimming competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job, Kirie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you helped hone my skills\Nthrough "Wii Wii Sports"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you can use that in real life...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You like the beach and stuff, and now\Nyou're a swimmer in The Game of Life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you'll be a pro swimmer and capture the gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it, but maybe\Ntalking about being a pro swimmer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Kirie might not like being told stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I've displeased my Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I, um, I'm sorry, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A storybook?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kirinrin."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, was it YOU who wrote this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I meant no disrespect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I mean... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to... to be a... storybook author!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A storybook author?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's a storybook author you've wanted to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awesome, Kirie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no! I-I'm sorry. I'm embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Naah, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna see it. What's it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,P-please forgive me, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shpaaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Sylphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning, Kirie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, are you aware what day it is today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,March 5th, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! And March 5th is Girls' Day,\Nwhen girls dress in traditional Japanese clothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure it's on March 3rd...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be over, but we can still wear our kimonos, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Note: On this day, elaborate dolls are put out on display.\NThat's right! And it's still okay to keep the dolls out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, right up until Insect Awakening Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, some areas keep them out\Nuntil the 4th... so, we're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylphin looks so different in a kimono, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always wearing the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, this year was the first time I've worn a kimono!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of us wore kimonos\Nat the department store one time, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I have a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shugaaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No! M-me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Squaring off against Sylphin makes Kirie rather active...\NLeaving me out is unfair indeed! I wish to take a photo as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving me out is unfair indeed! I wish to take a photo as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all four of us go take a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? We're not going to Nyaon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to go to a department store.\NWe can take a splendid photo at my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, my mother is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. Welcome back, Sylph.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so young!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, I am her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be Umaru, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Y-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Such elegance... such an aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All your body's numerical values\Nadhere to the golden ratio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly, it is the Divine Proportion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have some regimen to accentuate your beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! I want it, I want it, I want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bl-bleegh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,N-not especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Sylph?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we guide them to that room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother has won the\NAll-Japan Kimono Fitting Championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not unless I... am always the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed! Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're pretty similar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylph, your sleeves aren't aligned properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,W-well, I was moving around at school, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this not better?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad they get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina's hometown is in Akita,\Nso I bet she can't go back that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll have my mom teach me\Nhow to put on a kimono too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina, we have to put a little more force into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,SHBA!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shbababa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, that's my mother's high-speed\Nkimono fitting technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a tangible feeling of feminine power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And look, the dolls are still out on display.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Note: Sushi toppings scattered over a bowl of rice.\NWe have chirashizushi as well! Let's all eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say this calls for a photo. Come now, sit, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Say cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax and enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylphin, your mom is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not true. She just turned-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sylph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,INDEED!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awesome, Kirie!\NIt's like a book you'd see in the store!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No... the big sellers at Mujimuji Ryohin\Nare the ones that aren't too hard to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, I haven't got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This artwork still isn't enough to capture your grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cuteness! Your charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling of just wanting to hold you tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-that's why... I-I'd like to have you model for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Un modele?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Master! I'm sorry! That's fine for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I was no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a model sure is hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Master! Please, just act normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of the posing on my end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Still, I'll be thinking about you being there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Removing all trace of my presence is my special skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really a "special skill"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeak, squeak. Squeak, squeak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Master is right here in front of me, and she's so cute,\Nbut I just can't capture her expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a lack of my own abilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I'm sure that with more observation, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I must watch her even more closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,More closely...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,MORE CLOSELY!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaruuun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? Kirie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, Master! I didn't mean to wake you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Master Komaru is\NUmaru's younger sister, that was...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That was super fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to see you, Kirie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sorry for the bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. I got you a new flavor of potato chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A new flavor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're about to have dinner,\Nso you can't eat them today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Master's biggest smile is when her older brother is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie, you should join...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, join us for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I must go home and start drawing immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Drawing what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This says there's a new Western-style restaurant.\NHow about we have lunch there while we're shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna... sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That Umaru, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole spring break, all she's done is sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand that she's sleepy, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,she should dress up a little\Nand go have fun with her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Taihei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Ebina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty responsible of you\Nto always do the shopping yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all. Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, a new restaurant has opened up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We live in the same complex,\Nso I guess we do a lot of the same things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it might be the restaurant where my big brother works.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Ebina...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie, w-wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you, Kirie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,H-h-hello, Taihei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with all those pens?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be a storybook author!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,U-uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We use them a lot in art class.\NThey're always running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, they're for school, huh? That sure takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But it's spring break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I mean...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Big Brother went off to eat alone, did he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! There he is. And Kirie and Ebina?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea? How can you go off and eat alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you out with my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,W-well, I happened to run into him here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, it was at the supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie, are you buying those pens?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie, I bet you could totally be a storybook author...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...author...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it may be spring break, but we\Nuse them a lot in art class, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Art class?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something Kirie doesn't want us to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina saw that and has been trying to cover for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not talking to Umaru and Kirie\Nabout her big brother either...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she thinks she has to be careful\Nand not talk about these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really kind, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huuuuuuuh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great, isn't it, Ebina?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna turn the A/C on! I wanna turn the A/C on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's HOT, Big Brother! So hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still only May, so it's too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so hot last night that I couldn't sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And here, this is what YOU looked like!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you take that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's turn it on early this year! It won't cost that much\Nif we keep it up a little high.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm trying to say we're broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep the A/C on all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll stop being able to regulate your body heat\Nand you'll get cooling disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother! Big Brother! Big Brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how Big Brother sees me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we're not turning on the A/C till July!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's turned into some stubborn old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:19:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, stubborn old men are known\Nfor having a soft spot for kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure do know a lot, Big Brother.\NI'd never heard of cooling disorder!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, I just saw it on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be modest! You have SO much knowledge\Nto draw from that I'm jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she acting like some young performer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're always helping me with my studies.\NIt's such a big help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,R-really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So turn on the A/C.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I said no, and that means NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Big Brother, you're such a scrooge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ughhh... it's so hot. Big Brother, I can't sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.79,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? We had a fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bomba gave it to me last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Why didn't you bring it out sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. It was in the closet\Nand I completely forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get a nice breeze if we put it by the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot cooler than you'd think, huh?\NTonight, I can sleep in comfort!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Big Brother, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are shooting stars gonna shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we'll be seeing\Nany meteor showers this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There, you see those five stars\Nin a staggered pattern? That's Cassiopeia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what that glowing one there is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Altair. And next to that is Deneb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And over there, look. That bird-looking one is Cygnus.\NThe orange one is Arcturus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The white there is Spica.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't I taught you like this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'm imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru, do you know any other stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a mosquito, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a mosquito.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dream is so wonderful, Kirie!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.50,0:23:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worthy of such words, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.50,0:23:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You should let other people know about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I would like to ask your older sister about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.08,0:23:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. She'll be waiting.
